Text:
@globeplus, I didn't say anything bad about your pack. On the contrary, I'm sure it is working great, as I can see that you have experience with this emulator and you have uploaded many Wii games.

Nevertheless, new versions of the emulator with improvements and fixes are out daily. Thus it is good for the users to test new versions. But as you said we can keep your settings and just update the main emulator files.

Thanks and keep up the good work :)
